'''''Grenadier Models Inc.: 1987 Photographic Compendium''''' is a catalogue featuring photographs and figure listings of all the metal miniatures of [[Grenadier Models Inc.|Grenadier Models]] available at the time (it was published in [[1987]]). It features photographs and listings of all their ''Lord of the Rings'' figures.
